Name: Club Girl
About the game: Club Girl - You only need 4 keys (arrows), try to go through 10 levels, 10 different speeds, with each level the speed gets faster, one card (disco club), 10 different club soundtracks. A classic game, you need to press the arrow keys on your keyboard in time to earn points. Explosive soundtracks, explosive arrows, explosive combinations! Try it too! Features: Lots of animations Dynamic multi-angle camera 10 speeds (with each level the speed gets faster) 10 club soundtracks
